1498686502.text: "Our results indicate that LSS significantly protects from apoptotic injury to the cells induced by Abeta 25-35 (XREF_FIG, XREF_FIG and XREF_FIG), decreases mitochondria membrane potentials (XREF_FIG), upregulates the expression of Bcl-2 protein, and downregulates the expressions of Bax protein and the ratio of Bcl-2 and Bax (XREF_FIG), and inhibits the mRNA expression and nuclear translocation of NF-kappaBp65 (XREF_FIG and XREF_FIG) in Abeta 25-35 -treated PC12 cells."
